Code preview of 个人主体表sl_person_main

drop table if exists sl_person_main;

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: sl_person_main */
/*==============================================================*/
create table sl_person_main
(
personMainId bigint(20) not null auto_increment,
name varchar(50) character set utf8 not null comment '姓名',
sex smallint(6) not null comment '性别',
cardtype smallint(6) not null comment '证件类别',
cardnum varchar(100) character set utf8 not null comment '件号证码',
linktel varchar(50) character set utf8 not null comment '系电话联',
address varchar(250) comment '通讯地址',
tel varchar(50) character set utf8 comment '固定电话',
primary key (personMainId)
);

alter table sl_person_main comment '个人主体表';
